    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="个人博客搭建教程"><a href="#个人博客搭建教程" class="headerlink" title="个人博客搭建教程"></a>个人博客搭建教程</h1><p>参考文档：<a href="https://hexoscript.gitbook.io/hexo-script/">https://hexoscript.gitbook.io/hexo-script/</a></p><p>官网：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p><p>主题：<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></p><h2 id="1-1前期准备"><a href="#1-1前期准备" class="headerlink" title="1.1前期准备"></a>1.1前期准备</h2><p>1、注册github账号</p><p><a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com/</a></p><p>2、下载git软件</p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p><p>3、安装node.js环境</p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/</a></p><h2 id="1-2博客搭建"><a href="#1-2博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="1.2博客搭建"></a>1.2博客搭建</h2><p><strong>步骤</strong></p><p>新建一个文件夹<code>myblog</code>，用于下载hexo</p><p>1、脚本下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/kjhuanhao/hexo-script/releases">https://github.com/kjhuanhao/hexo-script/releases</a></p><p>2、本地环境检测</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source install.sh test_node  # 测试node环境</span><br><span class="line">source install.sh test_git  # 测试git环境</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3、下载hexo</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source install.sh hexo_win</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4、本地测试</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd hexoblog</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5、生成SSH密钥</p><p>在myblog目录下，生成密钥</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./install.sh git_ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6、公钥获取</p><p>用户目录下的.ssh文件夹</p><p>如：C:\Users\gmbjzg\.ssh</p><p>7、新建远程仓库</p><p>仓库名字格式要求：<code>用户名.github.io</code></p><p>8、配置信息</p><p>路径：<code>C:\Users\gmbjzg\Desktop\myblog\hexoblog\_config.yml</code></p><p>配置信息如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: 这里填你的仓库地址,建议使用SSH地址,它是以git开头的</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>9、生成上传脚本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source install.sh deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>10、部署到远程仓库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source up.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
